Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby appoint you to tutor my\Nson in the art of swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE] I expect\Ngreat things, swordmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NPrince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to teach you\Nall I know about the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning it will demand a great\Ndeal of effort from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To start, 1,000 push-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Though your first\Nattempts may falter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you will grow stronger in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain your stance.\NTry and keep your back upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] I emulate\NKing Bosse in my swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My style meets all foes\Nwith overwhelming force
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and never retreats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NSo what am I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] He is the one who's\Nsuffering the most in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NThat will be enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- [HILING] Domas.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] Does the boy have\Nany aptitude for the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still too soon to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NI see. Carry on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NDomas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sign language\Nhas greatly improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You may try it with Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] And do you believe\Nhe would be pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NHow should I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NPrince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Has everything been going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NHe understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Au-au, ee-uh, ah, ah-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji, you needn't\Nworry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be fine\Nexactly as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI swear to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE]\NQueen Hiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the judge from the Ranking\Nof Kings Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE] In the wake\Nof King Bosse's passing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,he is likely here to assess\Nthe kingdom's ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] It is a king's\Nduty to act decisively
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so that potential problems are\Nprevented before they occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those among your\Nsubjects who would treat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the first prince's presence\Nas a means to sow discord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,within the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the ensuing unrest would\Nundoubtedly claim many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty as\Nthe king is to avert
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,such catastrophes as these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the order to\Nassassinate Prince Bojji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NYes. As you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] With that done,\Nall that is left is to obtain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the strength of\NKing Bosse's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that really be necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Yes, for though\Nyou bear the vast potential
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of youth, King Daida,\Nthe power wielded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by King Bosse\Nwas without peer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NEven so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to stake my reign\Non my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[JUDGE 4A] How many years\Nhas it been now, Apeas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,From the committee, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It does take me back,\Nseeing you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLEM 4A growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[JUDGE 4A] Had we judged\Npurely on strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bosse would have\Nplaced first without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On the subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a few\Nunsavory rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been said that the king\Nwho ranks highest will be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,granted an item of his choosing\Nfrom the Divine Treasure Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[JUDGE 4A]\NIndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS] And that each\Nsuccessive king has chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the same treasure as the last,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,before either disappearing\Nor succumbing to madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that God grants them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[JUDGE 4A]\NThat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NIt's quite the prosperous town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Hmm. We should resupply\Nhere before moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now―\N[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Prince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[TROUPE 4A]\NAh! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[TROUPE 4B]\NSilence, you betrayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[TROUPE 4C]\NHold, villain! Now you face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold?! But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji...\NWhere are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Prince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stopping for a nap, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somebody take it from you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apology's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO whines]\NI'm so terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh, au, ah! Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mistakes\Nare our responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Prince Bojji, the people\Nhere work themselves ragged
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and endure great hardships\Nto make enough money to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must refrain from tempting\Nthem through displays of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Please learn your lesson\Nfrom this lapse in judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, did we have anything\Nof importance in that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We did. Queen Hiling gave us a\Nletter to deliver to her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's an issue!\N- I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize we― Gah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] If there's nothing\Nto be done, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. We should\Nget dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[JUDGE 4A]\NThough it pains me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your initial placement will be\Nlower than your predecessor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As of right now,\NI'd say around 90th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Are you prepared to\Nfollow any order handed down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from your superiors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of orders\Nwould they be giving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NWhatever kind they see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you obey them or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NI couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That shows a lack of resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those we serve bear\Npressures and responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond what you\Nor I could fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not for us to question\Nthe wisdom of their choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We are to enact their will\Nwith no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fair enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't considered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NNo. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NPrince Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of pressures\Nand responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,will you have to bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] The journey gets\Nmore dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't see\Nanother town for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NAh! Prince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that bag...\NIs it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is still in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEAST 4A growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh! Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NNo matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got your back\Nfrom now on, Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt, stranger!\NYou dare intrude on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah-au!\NEh-eh-au-au!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya-ya-ya! Ya-ya-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, uh, uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A] A denizen\Nof the mundane world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and what's more, you\Nseem unable to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you to this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A]\NIt compels you in its vastness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Its mystery draws you in.\NIts undeniable allure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOAR 4A squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As we offer up\Nthe flesh of this beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what we sacrifice is returned\Nto us many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A]\NCome and do as I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A] This is the dance\Nof reconciliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Through this rite, we seek the\Nforgiveness of those whose lives
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we take, and offer thanks for\Nthe sustenance they give.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, their bodies are\Nreturned to the forest anew
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to be sacrificed once\Nmore and sustain us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[HUNTER 4A]\NEat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good. Utterly delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious thing,\Nand yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this is in the nature\Nof all living beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We sacrifice the lives of\Nothers so we might feed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus sustain ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let me offer\Nyour life as my next sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NPrince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness!\NYou're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw the fire and came here.\NWe both feared the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NAh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NHere, Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NKeep alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's around,\Nbut they were just here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI can't sense anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who attacked, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some highwaymen, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[FOX 4A whining]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[FOX KITS squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a mother and her kits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NBebin! I recognize your knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hide! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO] The knives must have\Nbeen laced with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji.\NWe should bury them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Now they're\Nable to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, they'll be\Nhappy in the next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the town\Nwe will be passing through?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] There's a hole there\Nthat leads to the underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,called the Gates of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NThe Gates of Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the town seems\Nto be thriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always at peace, and the\Nmonsters never encroach,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all thanks to its protectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of the Underworld,\Nthe greatest knights in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Hokuro, find us\Na place to stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will escort you to see\Nthe Gates of Hell directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Every few minutes,\Nfrom this great chasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...an enormous pillar\Nof flame is released,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,like the fires of Hell itself\Nunleashed on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Come forward and look,\NPrince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not see the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji... forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I? What the―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NThat is Pandora's Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NMother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must open it,\Nfor if you don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you shall never\Nreign as a true king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Mirror! It's too dark.\NI can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NThat is hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] The only hope\Nyou have of finding salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NBrother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING, MAGIC MIRROR] After\Neach fall, he rises once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And with his unfaltering\Nheart, wards off calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't delay.
